[SHORT DESC]
Restores all PP to all of one Pokemon's moves.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Restores all PP to all of one Pokemon's moves.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Cannot be used in link or Wi-Fi battles.</p>

<h2>Location</h2>
<p>Route 8, Route 14, and Wellspring Cave (all with Dowsing Machine), Route 18, Dragonspiral Tower, Moor of Icirrus, Giant Chasm.</p>